Please read the README file before.

Plugin generation:
To create a plugin egg from sources just run:

python setup.py bdist_egg

which will create a .egg file in the dist directory.

GUI install:
Load the .egg file through the deluge plugin preferences page

Manual install:
Simply copy the .egg generated installation file to $HOME/.config/deluge/plugins

Install pyxmpp for the Jabber notification feature, on debian/ubuntu/linux-mint just type:
apt-get install python-pyxmpp